<br>
&quot;What the hell is wrong with me.. how can I of all people.. I be in love with some Ranger.. Why? .. I don't have much of a choice.. All of this has to leave.. No more House.. No more randomly killing..<br>
Well, maybe not. .. but what can I do.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Isn't about time you made your own? Shintou, I think you've proven here that you are different. Look about the world, and see yourself, you were never like those in that House, their noises high and their voice stained by Arogance to relize that hate can gather in places unknown to man.<br>
Shintou, gather this hate.. just like you saw it within your own love, you can find it in others. Gather it all together.<br>
